Step 1 - Click on services - Type EC2 in the search bar
Step 2 - Click Load balancer
Step 3 - Click create new - Choose HTTP, HTTPS
Step 4 - Specify details
Step 5 - Thick all boxes 1a-1f
Step 6 - Choose ELB security group
Step 7 - Add tags, review and create
Step 8 - Successfully created load balancer
Step 9 - Go back to instances, Click actions - Click image & template - create image
Step 10 - Input details - image name and description - click create image
Step 11 - Click AMI from the left pane and edit the name
Step 12 - Click autoscaling on the left pane
